              Hey! 👋 I'm your <strong>CS1101 Study Buddy</strong>. I know everything in Prof. Wang's syllabus — grades, deadlines, policies, topics, and more!<br><br>What can I help you with today? 🎉
            </div>
            <span class="source-ref">📄 CS1101 Syllabus · WPU</span>
          </div>
        </div>
