      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>CS1101 Study Buddy · Built for students at <a href="https://www.wpunj.edu" target="_blank">William Paterson University</a> · Not an official university tool · Always verify with Prof. Wang</p>
  </footer>

</div>

<script>
const SYLLABUS = `
COURSE: CS1101 - AI for Everyone
INSTRUCTOR: Nan Wang
OFFICE: George and Dorothy Hennings Science Hall East, Room #5029
OFFICE HOURS: Tuesdays & Thursdays 1:00 PM - 2:00 PM, Wednesday 1:00 PM - 3:00 PM, By Appointment (in-person or ZOOM)
EMAIL: wangn1@wpunj.edu (preferred: email or Blackboard message)
ZOOM: https://wpunj.zoom.us/my/nan.wang.wpu (Passcode: havefun)
CLASSROOM: Hennings Science Hall East Room 5035
CLASS TIME: Monday and Wednesday 5:00 PM - 6:15 PM
